{"type": "article", "id": 6753, "title": "Infinitum 桌子", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-25T07:18:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234230BGUAuwjVPELqdDey.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t纽约设计师 Lousie-anne Van ‘t Riet 最近接到了一个特殊的邀请，任务是要他利用开放资源电子平台 Arduino 进行设计，而他带来的是一款名为「Infinitum」的桌子，其最大的特点是能够发光。Lousie-anne Van ‘t Riet 的意图是希望借由这款会发光的桌子提醒用户日常生活中注意随时清理桌子，当桌子上一旦有东西，桌面的灯光就会自动点亮，成为桌上物品的灯光背景 ，直至物品被清理干净或拿掉时，桌面的灯光才会熄灭。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234227qMOuWFYQomx8hbED.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234228JX4g2pYy631zmtSO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234228ABEKDsxk5eoIaRHr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234228oVSI6J57Ygmxp1yT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234229BqsM3wxPO5hXN86D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}